               <msContents>
                  <summary>Homiliary for the Monthly Feast of the Archangel Michael, ድርሳነ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Five Pillars of Mystery, brief version, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡</summary>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="5r" facs="002">Fols 1r–5r</locus>
                <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="5r" to="5r" facs="006">Fols 5r–5r</locus>
                <title>Greeting to the Archangel Michael</title>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  [ሰላም፡] ለከ፡ መልአከ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ወግርማ፡
                  ዓቃቤ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ እምፃማ።
                  ቅንአተ፡ እሳት፡ ወመብረቅ፡ ዘራማ።
                  መዐርኢረ፡ ዜማ፡
                </incipit>
                </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="6r" to="71v" facs="007">Fols 6r–71v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1295Dersan">Dǝrsāna
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>

                <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.1"><locus from="6r" to="8v" facs="007">Fols 6r–8v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1295Dersa#Introductionn"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1295Dersa, could not check for Introductionn</span></title></msItem>
